# Security Review Guidelines
- Review code for common security vulnerabilities such as SQL injection and XSS.
- Ensure proper handling of sensitive data and credentials.
- Validate user inputs to prevent security breaches.
- Keep dependencies updated to mitigate known security issues.

# Security Review Checklist
- [ ] Review code for common security vulnerabilities
- [ ] Ensure proper handling of sensitive data and credentials
- [ ] Validate user inputs to prevent security breaches
- [ ] Keep dependencies updated to mitigate known security issues

# Security Review Tools
- [Bandit](https://github.com/PyCQA/bandit) - Python security linter
- [eslint](https://eslint.org/) - JavaScript linter
- [OWASP Dependency Check](https://jeremylong.github.io/DependencyCheck/) - Dependency checker
- [OWASP ZAP](https://www.zaproxy.org/) - Web application security scanner
